interestingcomments.content: To clarify the thing about dust on the new sensor, in this image all spots are colored in white and in the exact size of the dust spots and the image is uncropped. To me this is too much, what do you think? At a distance of around 50 meters, a spot is as big as a sitting seagull... /magnus --img--  Edited June 2, 2019 by Magnus_L_Andersson
